<template>
  <v-container fluid>
    <v-col></v-col>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>

// SERVICES
import SrvSeries from '@/services/srv-series'

export default {
    name: "InitHome",
    data() {
        return {
            dItems:[]
        }
    },
    created(){
        this.fIniciarVariables()
    },
    methods:{
        fIniciarVariables(){
            this.fGetPopulares()
        },
        fGetPopulares(){
            let payload = {
                params: {
                    api_key: process.env.API_KEY_IMAGENES,
                    language: 'es-ES',
                    page: 1
                }
            }
            console.log(payload)
            SrvSeries.getTvSeries(payload).then(respuesta => {
                console.log("Respuesta")
                console.log(respuesta)
            })
        }
    }
}
</script>

</style>
